  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Quadulo</i> is a fresh and addictive puzzle game where you slide rows and columns to connect blocks of the same color. Build islands by connecting all blocks of a color and solve puzzles by completing all the islands. Simple to learn, challenging to master, and endlessly satisfying!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962090/extras/dc826576f337368d5f15a969232341fd.poster.avif?t=1741124024\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962090/extras/dc826576f337368d5f15a969232341fd.webm?t=1741124024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962090/extras/dc826576f337368d5f15a969232341fd.mp4?t=1741124024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>Unique Gameplay</strong>: Strategically move blocks to form color islands.<br>🎨 <strong>Vivid Design</strong>: Distinct, vibrant colors for clarity and focus.<br>🎮 <strong>Multiple Modes</strong>: Growth, Mastery, and Custom modes to suit every mood.<br>📈 <strong>Engaging Progression</strong>: Unlock larger puzzles and new mechanics as you advance.<br>✨ <strong>Balanced Fun</strong>: Relaxing yet rewarding puzzles for all skill levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962090/extras/656438cc1f8c9e7aaeee48dc07ad8cda.poster.avif?t=1741124024\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962090/extras/656438cc1f8c9e7aaeee48dc07ad8cda.webm?t=1741124024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962090/extras/656438cc1f8c9e7aaeee48dc07ad8cda.mp4?t=1741124024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect. Strategize. Build.<br><strong>Play Quadulo today!</strong></p>",
